

man                   Technical Information                   man




Manual macro package

nnrrooffff -mmaann _f_i_l_e ...

The nroff macro package man  formats manual pages in the style of
the Lexicon.  It includes the following macros:


     .BB  Boldface font.
     .BBII Bold/italic alternating fonts.
     .BBRR Bold/Roman alternating fonts.
     .CCOO COHERENT.
     .DDEE Display end.
     .DDSS Display start.
     .DDTT Default tabs.
     .HHEE Help end.
     .HHPP Hanging paragraph.
     .HHSS Help start.
     .II  Italic font.
     .IIBB Italic/bold alternating fonts.
     .IIPP Indented paragraph.
     .IIRR Italic/Roman alternating fonts.
     .LLPP Paragraph, flush left.
     .PPDD Paragraph distance.
     .PPPP Paragraph, indented.
     .RRBB Roman/bold alternating fonts.
     .RREE Relative indent end.
     .RRII Roman/italic alternating fonts.
     .RRSS Relative indent start.
     .SSHH Subheader.
     .SSMM Smaller size.
     .TTHH Header.
     .TTPP Tagged paragraph.


